goal.ch:
1. 養成自學習慣，並培養更完整之英語運用能力及信心;
2. 應用基本閱讀技巧，並能正確無誤地解讀文章之寓意，進而做推論;
3. 閱讀科學、社會人文、語文學習等不同領域的英文文章，並掌握其內容；
4. 養成閱讀課外讀物的興趣與泛讀的習慣。

goal.en:
On successful completion of this course, students will be able to:
1. Demonstrate the ability of lifelong self-learning;
2. Use basic reading skills, such as skimming for main ideas, scanning for specific information, and guessing meaning from the context, to understand the main idea, and make inferences/predictions from the text;
3. Read and understand articles in different subject areas, such as science, social studies and language arts;
4. Appreciate the joys of reading, and develop the interests of extensive reading.
